description:
The Seventh Day before Christmas: Episode Three is narrated by Elizabeth, a close relative of Mary. Elizabeth miraculously conceived of John the Baptist, so she was completely prepared for Mary to have a miraculous birth, too.

Elizabeth tells of her miraculous pregnancy, and the birth of her son, John the Baptist. She says that he will be the one to prepare the way for the coming Messiah.

Eyewitness Bible Series is pleased to present the Christmas Series. This series is a collection of 10 new episodes designed to be watched on the three Sundays prior to Christmas week, plus the seven days of Christmas week, ending on Christmas Day.

Scripture: Luke 1
